---
import ArrowEntry from "@/components/custom/arrowEntry.astro"
import Layout from "@/layouts/main.astro"
---

<Layout>
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-20 z-10 -translate-y-1/2">
    <h3 class="font-marker text-muted-foreground">Who</h3>
    <h1 class="font-marker text-9xl tracking-widest text-primary">AM I?</h1>

    <div class="mt-8 max-w-2xl space-y-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground">
      <p>
        I am TFJ, an IT Specialist apprentice for Application Development.
        Basically, I turn caffeine into code and hope for the best (well
        actually I just drink water).
      </p>

      <p>
        When I'm not "apprenticing" (which is a fancy word for learning why my
        code broke), I'm working on side projects that may or may not ever see
        the light of day.
      </p>

      <p>
        I have a deep-seated love for the Cyberpunk genre—mostly because it
        predicts a future where my bad eyesight can be fixed with cool neon
        implants.
      </p>

      <p>
        As for the domain <code class="text-primary">thekoi.dev</code>? I find
        fish fascinating, especially Kois. They just swim around, look pretty,
        and don't have to deal with merge conflicts. Living the dream, honestly.
      </p>
    </div>

    <ul class="mt-12 max-w-md space-y-2">
      <ArrowEntry link="/links" className="block h-full w-full">
        You may know me from
      </ArrowEntry>
      <ArrowEntry link="/about" className="block h-full w-full">
        Back to About
      </ArrowEntry>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Layout>
